text.tspan: Each replica node in DC jfk sends the write request to its backend.
Remote coordinator on jfk-r1-s1 (which is 1 of 3 remote replicas) forwards write request to
backend on its server and to the other two replicas in DC jfk.
Coordinator forwards write request to replicas in local DC and
to remote coordinator in DC jfk.
Coordinator on sfo-r1-s1 forwards write request to its backend.
Client sends write request (CL = dc_one) to a replica node.
